  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 12 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "12 people who tried to go to Australia illegally were arrested in Vadamarachi",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "12 people who tried to travel illegally to Australia have been arrested by the San Pedro police.",
        "The police have arrested Vadamaratsi in a house near East Manatkadu Beach this Saturday morning.",
        "8 men and 4 women were arrested in the house where they were staying",
        "All the 12 arrested persons have been taken to Parutthurai Police Station and preliminary investigations are underway."
      ],
